*Izraz* mu je iskazao nezadovoljstvo. (He expressed his dissatisfaction.)

Njegov *izraz* lica je govorio da je ljut. (His facial expression showed that he was angry.)

Ona je *izrazito* hladna prema meni. (She was extremely cold to me.)

Njegovo ponašanje je *izraz* nepoštovanja. (His behavior was an expression of disrespect.)

Ona je *izrazito* ponosna. (She was extremely proud.)